Are you ready?

00:11:01.890 --> 00:11:02.120
JOSH SASSOON: Yes.

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:03.078
MICHAEL AUSTIN SUI: OK.

00:11:03.078 --> 00:11:04.480
So it's flex and fit.

00:11:04.480 --> 00:11:07.580
So choose words that are
flexible in their definition

00:11:07.580 --> 00:11:11.600
yet specific enough to
actually work and be useful.

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:15.010
And then once you get them, you
can dial them up or dial them

00:11:15.010 --> 00:11:17.717
down depending on the context
of your project or your work

00:11:17.717 --> 00:11:19.300
or the problem you're
trying to solve.

00:11:19.300 --> 00:11:20.091
JOSH SASSOON: Cool.

00:11:20.091 --> 00:11:23.190
And last but not least, think
principles before pixels.

00:11:23.190 --> 00:11:25.540
Stay true to your community
by turning those brand

00:11:25.540 --> 00:11:27.610
attributes into
actionable principles

00:11:27.610 --> 00:11:30.020
that you measure all of
your design work against.

